WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.460
Normal Grey: Not once, not twice, but thrice in American History,

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:06.740
the candidate with the most votes from the people actually lost because of the Electoral College.

00:00:06.780 --> 00:00:09.420
Exasperated Grey: Four times now, this has happened four times.

00:00:09.480 --> 00:00:13.760
Normal Grey: Three errors in fifty-five plus elections is a failure rate of five percent.

00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:15.060
Exasperated Grey: Seven percent.

00:00:15.180 --> 00:00:18.220
Normal Grey: Would anyone tolerate a sport where by a quirk of the rules there was a-

00:00:18.220 --> 00:00:19.020
Exasperated Grey: Seven percent.

00:00:19.040 --> 00:00:21.560
Normal Grey: -chance that the loser would win? Not likely.

